      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of a well-loved daily driver that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior maintains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, superficial scratch near the rear wheel well\u2014typical for a car of this age but overall very presentable. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free. The premium leather seats are supple and comfortable; while the driver\u2019s side bolster shows some light creasing from entry and exit, there are no tears or fading. All onboard electronics, including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control, function exactly as they should. Mechanically, the car is in solid health. It starts up immediately with a smooth idle and pulls strongly through all gears. I have stayed ahead of the maintenance schedule, recently completing a full synthetic oil change and a brake fluid flush. The tires have plenty of life left, and the alloy wheels are free of significant curb rash. This is a turn-key vehicle that offers a reliable and refined driving experience for its next owner.",
